@host = https://httpbin.org
@token = my-secret-token
@user_id = 123

### Test with variables
GET {{host}}/get
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-User-ID: {{user_id}}

### Test with dynamic variables
POST {{host}}/post
Content-Type: application/json
X-Request-ID: {{$uuid}}
X-Timestamp: {{$timestamp}}
X-Random: {{$randomInt}}

{
  "user_id": "{{user_id}}",
  "timestamp": {{$timestamp}},
  "random_value": {{$randomInt}}
}

### Test environment variable
GET {{host}}/headers
X-Home-Dir: {{$processEnv.HOME}}
